{
  "id": "adv_event_2306_02_03",
  "title": "STAGE3",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_03-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "ご覧いただき、ありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for watching.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8000001291,
      "endTime": 3.6938550332999998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_03-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "LizNoirで\n『The Last Chance』でした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was LizNoir's\n\"The Last Chance.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.9000001291,
      "endTime": 7.1257143835,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.3333334624
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_03-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "今日は日頃の感謝を込めて\n{user}さんとさとみさんにこの曲を――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today‚ with our usual gratitude‚\nwe dedicate this song to {user}-san and Satomi-san――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.3333334624,
      "endTime": 12.240069216,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.3666666685
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_03-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "ストップ、ストーーーップ！！！\n前置きが長過ぎです！　こころにMCチェンジです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Stop‚ stoooop―!!\nIt's been too long! Kokoro is taking a mic as a MC!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.3666666685,
      "endTime": 18.9765760122,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.1666666685
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_03-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "いいじゃないか、これくらい喋らせてあげても\nとめどない感謝が溢れているんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Would it be okay to let her say a few words?\nWe're overflowing with endless gratitude‚ after all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.1666666685,
      "endTime": 25.4307255445,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.6333333352
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_03-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "確かに……莉央さん、お二人への感謝の言葉\nギリギリまで考えていましたよね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really… Rio-chan‚ You were deliberating\nuntil the very end what words you would say to them!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.6333333352,
      "endTime": 32.1729025224,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.3666666685
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_03-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "サラッと莉央さんをいじる愛ちゃん、いいですねぇ\nそんなに考えても尺が足りませんよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I like teasing Rio-chan a bit‚ it's fun\nNo matter how much you deliberate‚ time runs short~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.3666666685,
      "endTime": 39.2393652617,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.4333333352
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_03-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "なのでここはこころが――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ here's Kokoro――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.4333333352,
      "endTime": 41.2201814034,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.4000012735
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_03-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "ライブの選曲は、それぞれグループで行ったのだから\n選曲基準もグループごとに異なるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since each group had their own live selection\nThe selection criteria varied for each group",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.4000012735,
      "endTime": 47.6940374711,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.9000012735
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_03-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "華麗なスルー！\nですが、こころはめげません！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A dazzling pass!\nBut‚ Kokoro won't back down!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.9000012735,
      "endTime": 52.1192529539,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.3333346068
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_03-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "リズノワは、好きな曲を話し合ったんだけど\nみんなバラバラで全然決まらなくてね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We talked about our favorite songs from LizNoir‚\nbut everyone's preferences were different‚ so we couldn't decide.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.3333346068,
      "endTime": 58.3304547964,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.5333346068
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_03-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "だから莉央さんが{user}さんに\nリズノワの楽曲の中で一番好きな曲を教えてくれる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's why Rio-chan asked\n\"Which song from LizNoir do you like the most?\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.5333346068,
      "endTime": 65.0061690031,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.4000001291
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_03-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "って直接聞きに行ったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "to {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.2000012735,
      "endTime": 67.83170183690001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_03-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "はあ……でも貴方が「全部好き」なんて言うから\nまた振り出しに戻ったのよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… but when you said you like 'all of them‚'\nDidn't we go back to square one?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.0333346068,
      "endTime": 74.4865318953,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 68.0333346068
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.7000012735
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_03-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "君が全ての楽曲について熱く語り出した時は\n僕も驚いたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When you passionately spoke about every song‚\nI was surprised too",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.7000012735,
      "endTime": 79.69276793990001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.9000012735
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_03-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "聞いてるこっちが恥ずかしかったです～\n途中から莉央さんの顔も真っ赤になってましたし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We felt embarrassed listening to it~\nAnd Rio-chan's face even turned red",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.9000012735,
      "endTime": 86.2003412584,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.4000012735
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_03-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっ、こころ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait a moment‚ Kokoro!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.4000012735,
      "endTime": 88.00836864509999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.2000012735
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "わ、悪かったな……\nそれで、どうしてこの曲を選んでくれたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-Sorry…\nSo‚ why did you choose this song?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.2000012735,
      "endTime": 94.1996839861,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.4000012735
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_03-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "お二人に伝えたい想いが一番こもっている曲を\n選ぼうってことになったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We chose a song that best conveys\nour hearts to you both.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.4000012735,
      "endTime": 99.9674616197,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.1666679401
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_03-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "そしたら満場一致の多数決で\n『The Last Chance』に決まったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So unanimously‚\nWe decided on 『The Last Chance』.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.1666679401,
      "endTime": 105.4000001291,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.5999992389
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_03-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "これから先もきっと、今まで以上に大変で\n予測不可能なことが沢山あると思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There will undoubtedly be more difficult and\nunpredictable times ahead.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.5999992389,
      "endTime": 112.1647611636,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 112.3666659056
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_02_03-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "それでも私達LizNoirは\n四人で抱いた夢を叶えるために前に進んでいきます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But LizNoir will continue\nto strive towards the dream held by the four of us!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.3666659056,
      "endTime": 119.3618358313,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119.5666659056
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
